    <item>
      <title>拜登警告以色列公众舆论可能会在哈马斯战争中发生转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/biden-warns-israel-that-public-opinion-can-shift-in-hamas-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登警告说，支持以色列对抗哈马斯的公众舆论可能会发生变化，因为他试图平衡自己对以色列的支持与要求以色列限制加沙平民伤亡的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/biden-warns-israel-that-public-opinion-can-shift-in-hamas-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 01:06:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾呼吁美国支持保护银行免受网络攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/taiwan-calls-on-us-support-to-defend-banks-against-cyberattacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾的金融体系支撑着价值 7600 亿美元的高科技经济，但其容易遭受高级黑客攻击，引发了人们对最坏情况的担忧：来自中国的全面网络攻击，导致台湾货币和市场陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/taiwan-calls-on-us-support-to-defend-banks-against-cyberattacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院表示将迅速就特朗普豁免案采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/supreme-court-signals-quick-call-on-doj-bid-to-fast-track-trump-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院表示，将迅速决定是否干预因唐纳德·特朗普因试图推翻 2020 年总统选举而受到刑事指控而引发的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/supreme-court-signals-quick-call-on-doj-bid-to-fast-track-trump-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 22:59:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登称枪支、税务案件在交易失败后无效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/hunter-biden-s-lawyers-argue-he-s-immune-to-gun-tax-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登的律师在法庭文件中辩称，亨特·拜登不应面临联邦税收和枪支指控，因为他在 7 月份与联邦检察官达成的失败认罪协议仍然具有约束力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/hunter-biden-s-lawyers-argue-he-s-immune-to-gun-tax-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 22:06:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平自2017年以来首次访问越南以对抗美国影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/xi-makes-first-vietnam-visit-in-six-years-to-counter-us-clout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当中国国家主席习近平六年来首次访问越南时，他将寻求确保这个具有重要战略意义的亚洲伙伴不会与美国走得太近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/xi-makes-first-vietnam-visit-in-six-years-to-counter-us-clout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>化肥行业面临农民支持的美国法案审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/fertilizer-industry-sway-is-focus-of-upcoming-us-legislation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在打击肉类行业集中化之后，美国参议员现在希望政府审查化肥公司的权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/fertilizer-industry-sway-is-focus-of-upcoming-us-legislation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 20:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙首席执行官认为委内瑞拉和圭亚那对话比战争更有可能</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/chevron-ceo-wirth-downplays-risk-of-venezuelan-military-conflict-with-guyana</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司高管表示，尽管南美国家之间的敌对言论日益增多，但委内瑞拉和圭亚那之间的边界争端不太可能升级为军事冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/chevron-ceo-wirth-downplays-risk-of-venezuelan-military-conflict-with-guyana</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 19:17:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孕妇在州最高法院判决前离开德克萨斯州堕胎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-11/urgent-texas-woman-who-sought-court-permission-for-abortion-leaves-state-for-the-procedure-attorneys-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州奥斯汀（美联社）——一名胎儿患有致命疾病的得克萨斯州孕妇离开该州前往其他地方堕胎，周一该州最高法院驳回了她对美国最严格禁令之一提出的史无前例的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-11/urgent-texas-woman-who-sought-court-permission-for-abortion-leaves-state-for-the-procedure-attorneys-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 19:11:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸称中国帮助斡旋与叛军联盟进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/myanmar-says-china-helping-broker-talks-with-rebel-alliance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸执政军政府表示，中国正在帮助斡旋与反叛组织联盟的讨论，该联盟近几个月来加大了边境地区的袭击力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/myanmar-says-china-helping-broker-talks-with-rebel-alliance</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 13:19:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚不能排除向哈马斯提供数百万捐款的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/malaysia-can-t-rule-out-if-millions-in-donations-went-to-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情官员透露，马来西亚政府不能排除当地一家慈善机构是否向哈马斯输送了数百万美元，目前正在调查该组织涉嫌支持东南亚国家的保守派伊斯兰组织。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-11/malaysia-can-t-rule-out-if-millions-in-donations-went-to-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Dec 2023 08:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
